25:[["$","blockquote",null,{"children":["\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"阅读提示\n适合对象：需要用 tcpdump 和 Wireshark 做排障、取证和告警分析的读者。\n阅读前提：了解 TCP/IP、常见端口和基础抓包概念。\n核心收获：提升抓包、过滤、重放和流量还原的实战效率。\n说明：不同版本的过滤表达式和界面细节可能存在差异。"}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"网络流量分析是安全运维和故障排查的核心技能。通过抓包工具捕获和分析网络数据包，可以发现异常通信、诊断网络问题、检测恶意行为和验证安全策略。本文将深入讲解 tcpdump 和 Wireshark 两款最重要的抓包分析工具的使用方法，并通过实战场景演示流量分析技巧。"}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"网络抓包原理","children":["网络抓包原理",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#网络抓包原理","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"混杂模式promiscuous-mode","children":["混杂模式（Promiscuous Mode）",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#混杂模式promiscuous-mode","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":["网络接口默认只接收目标为自身 MAC 地址的数据帧。开启混杂模式后，网卡会接收经过接口的",["$","strong",null,{"children":"所有数据帧"}],"，这是网络抓包的基础。在交换网络中，通常需要配合端口镜像（Port Mirroring / SPAN）才能捕获其他主机的流量。"]}],"\n","$L2d","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"bpf-过滤器berkeley-packet-filter","children":["BPF 过滤器（Berkeley Packet Filter）",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#bpf-过滤器berkeley-packet-filter","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"BPF 是 BSD 系统引入的内核级包过滤机制。tcpdump 和 Wireshark 的捕获过滤器都基于 BPF 语法。BPF 在内核层面进行过滤，只将匹配的数据包复制到用户空间，大幅减少了性能开销。"}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":["BPF 过滤表达式由**原语（Primitives）**组合而成，支持逻辑运算符 ",["$","code",null,{"children":"and"}],"（",["$","code",null,{"children":"&&"}],"）、",["$","code",null,{"children":"or"}],"（",["$","code",null,{"children":"||"}],"）、",["$","code",null,{"children":"not"}],"（",["$","code",null,{"children":"!"}],"）。"]}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"tcpdump-常用命令与过滤表达式","children":["tcpdump 常用命令与过滤表达式",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#tcpdump-常用命令与过滤表达式","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"tcpdump 是 Linux/Unix 环境下最经典的命令行抓包工具，几乎所有服务器都预装了它。"}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"基础命令","children":["基础命令",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#基础命令","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L2e","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"ip-地址和网段过滤","children":["IP 地址和网段过滤",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#ip-地址和网段过滤","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L2f","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"端口过滤","children":["端口过滤",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#端口过滤","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L30","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"协议过滤","children":["协议过滤",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#协议过滤","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L31","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"tcp-标志位过滤","children":["TCP 标志位过滤",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#tcp-标志位过滤","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L32","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"高级组合过滤","children":["高级组合过滤",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#高级组合过滤","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L33","\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"wireshark-过滤器详解","children":["Wireshark 过滤器详解",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#wireshark-过滤器详解","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"Wireshark 是最强大的图形化抓包分析工具，支持两种不同的过滤器。"}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"捕获过滤器capture-filter","children":["捕获过滤器（Capture Filter）",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#捕获过滤器capture-filter","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"在捕获前设置，使用 BPF 语法，作用于内核层面。与 tcpdump 语法完全相同。"}],"\n","$L34","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"显示过滤器display-filter","children":["显示过滤器（Display Filter）",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#显示过滤器display-filter","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"在捕获后对已抓取的数据包进行过滤显示，语法更丰富、更强大。"}],"\n","$L35","\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"实战流量分析场景","children":["实战流量分析场景",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#实战流量分析场景","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"分析-tcp-三次握手","children":["分析 TCP 三次握手",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#分析-tcp-三次握手","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L36","\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"正常的三次握手过程："}],"\n",["$","ol",null,{"children":["\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"SYN"}],"：客户端 → 服务器，",["$","code",null,{"children":"Seq=0, Flags=[S]"}]]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":["$L37","：服务器 → 客户端，","$L38"]}],"\n","$L39","\n"]}],"\n","$L3a","\n","$L3b","\n","$L3c","\n","$L3d","\n","$L3e","\n","$L3f","\n","$L40","\n","$L41","\n","$L42","\n","$L43","\n","$L44","\n","$L45","\n","$L46","\n","$L47","\n","$L48","\n","$L49","\n","$L4a","\n","$L4b","\n","$L4c","\n","$L4d","\n","$L4e","\n","$L4f","\n","$L50","\n","$L51","\n","$L52","\n","$L53","\n","$L54","\n","$L55","\n","$L56","\n","$L57","\n","$L58","\n","$L59","\n","$L5a","\n","$L5b","\n","$L5c","\n","$L5d"]
